DESCRIPTION

FLSDK v0.0.3 is a collection of Bash scripts designed to assist
users in compiling the various FLDIGI applications used by
Amateur Radio Operators.


INSTALL INSTRUCTIONS

Download:
* Download flsdk-<version>.tar.gz

Extract:
* tar -xf flsdk-<version>.tar.gz
* cd ./flsdk-<version>

Configure, make, make install:
* ./autogen.sh
* make
* sudo make isntall


RUN FLSDK
* Open A Terminal, then type: flsdk


SUPPORT

If you have problems with the FLSDK, please email <ki7mt01@gmail.com>

